- remove test programs from "all' target
- lmdbg-grep: -f <n> output n first stacktraces
- lmdbg-grep: -l <n> output n last stacktraces
- lmdbg-sym: option to NOT generate source.c:NN or funcname component
- lmdbg-run: option for skipping addresses from the end
- lmdbg-run: always prepand addresses with 0x?
- lmdbg-run: -n for numbering all memory allocations
- lmdbg-leaks: native order of leaks, earlier allocated -- earlier in output
- LMDBG_AWK - preferred AWK interpreter
- 'info time <minutes>'
- SIGUSR1 (LMDBG_SIG_LOG) for starting logging, lmdbg-run -d
- lmdbg-m2s and lmdbg-s2m --> /usr/local/libexec/lmdbg/
- lmdbg-leaks written in C (libJudy)
- lmdbg-leaks: double free
